1- Docker root Dir:    /var/lib/docker        ==>> the place where Containers are Running

registry:  the place where "RESTORE the Images"
        1)  Publuic  (Online)
        2)  Private  (Online OR LOCAL)
Docker Hub:  Public Docker Registry

Image:  is the Template OR The Source Of the app with its Dependencies,          the Image is Compressed and Read-Only

Engine:  the service that Provide Container Layer,   and enable me to create Containers  & Manage Containers (Run/Stop)

  
Container:  Running App inside Isolated Environment with Dependencies

client OR cli (cli prefer to  Client OR Command Line Interface):  it provide the Tools or Commands to be able to talk o the Engine  (Start/Stop/Create....)
